lead_paragraph: Panthers coach Ron Rivera is not worried about losing the faith of his players in the locker room after his decision to bench Cam Newton for the start of Sunday night's game against the Seattle Seahawks.

headline.print_headline: Rivera Not Worried About Losing Team After Benching Newton
headline.main: Rivera Not Worried About Losing Team After Benching Newton
